### Get all habits
GET http://localhost:5000/api/habits

### Create a new habit
POST http://localhost:5000/api/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Exercise"
}

### Update a habit (replace HABIT_ID with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/habits/HABIT_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### Delete a habit (replace HABIT_ID with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/habits/HABIT_ID
